#Hypertension is a condition in which the blood pressure is abnormally high.
Exercise, use of certain drugs, anxiety, etc are factors that can increase the blood pressure in a normal person. #hypertension
#Hypertension therefore is diagnosed when the blood pressure AT REST reads >140/90mmHg on two different occasions, at least 6 hours apart.
